metadata.name: Flying Fish  | Haleek Maul - VERIFIED Moments x DOOMSDAYX
metadata.description:
A 360° unseen view, 1/1 collectible from the music video VERIFIED feat. Chiief Diin by Haleek Maul.

The flying fish scene was one of the most graphically challenging scenes for the VFX team; creating the appearance of Haleek standing in an endless ocean with fish flying all around him.

Fact: Barbados is known as "the land of the flying fish and is native to the island.
